.TH MATERIATRACK 1 "November 2024" "MatteriaTrack 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
materiatrack \- Final Fantasy-themed time tracking CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B materiatrack
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B MatteriaTrack
is a mystical, Final Fantasy-themed power user time tracking CLI based on Zeit.
Track your time with style, earn achievements, and master your productivity destiny.
.PP
"Master your time, master your destiny"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-config " " \fIPATH\fR
Configuration file path
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format: pretty, json, plain, statusbar (default: pretty)
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose
Verbose output
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Print help information
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-version
Print version information
.SH COMMANDS
.SS Tracking
.TP
.B track \-p PROJECT \-t TASK
Start tracking time on a task
.TP
.B finish
Finish the current tracking session
.TP
.B status
Show current tracking status
.TP
.B switch
Quick switch between projects/tasks (fuzzy finder)
.SS Listing
.TP
.B list
Show recent tracked entries
.TP
.B list \-\-since DATE
Filter entries by date
.TP
.B list \-\-total
Show time totals
.SS Projects & Tasks
.TP
.B project add NAME
Create new project
.TP
.B project list
Show all projects
.TP
.B task add NAME \-p PROJECT
Create new task in project
.TP
.B task list
Show all tasks
.SS Statistics
.TP
.B stats
Show time statistics
.TP
.B stats \-\-today
Today's statistics
.TP
.B stats \-\-week
This week's statistics
.TP
.B stats \-\-month
This month's statistics
.SS Integration
.TP
.B statusbar
Output for DWM/i3/Polybar statusbar
.TP
.B dashboard
Launch interactive TUI dashboard
.TP
.B export \-\-export\-format FORMAT
Export data (json, csv)
.TP
.B import \-\-zeit PATH
Import from Zeit database
.SS Achievements
.TP
.B achievements
Show achievements and progress
.SS Configuration
.TP
.B config show
Show current configuration
.TP
.B config path
Show configuration file path
.TP
.B config edit
Edit configuration in $EDITOR
.TP
.B completions SHELL
Generate shell completions (bash, zsh, fish)
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Start tracking a task:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack track \-p "MatteriaTrack" \-t "Development"
.fi
.RE
.PP
Finish with time adjustment:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack finish \-\-end="\-0:15"
.fi
.RE
.PP
Start tracking 15 minutes ago:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack track \-p "Project" \-t "Task" \-\-begin="\-0:15"
.fi
.RE
.PP
Show today's statistics:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack stats \-\-today
.fi
.RE
.PP
Export to JSON:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack export \-\-export\-format json \-\-output data.json
.fi
.RE
.PP
Launch dashboard:
.RS
.nf
materiatrack dashboard
.fi
.RE
.SH THEMES
MatteriaTrack supports 6 elemental Materia themes:
.TP
.B Fire
Burning passion and fierce determination (red/orange)
.TP
.B Ice
Cool precision and crystalline clarity (blue/cyan)
.TP
.B Lightning
Electric energy and swift action (yellow/purple)
.TP
.B Earth
Grounded strength and natural growth (green/brown)
.TP
.B Wind
Ethereal freedom and endless possibility (white/gray)
.TP
.B Bahamut
Ultimate power and legendary mastery (dark purple/gold)
.PP
Set theme in config.toml:
.RS
.nf
[ui]
theme = "bahamut"
.fi
.RE
.SH ACHIEVEMENTS
Earn achievements as you track your time:
.TP
.B Materia Equipped
Create your first tracked entry
.TP
.B Limit Break
Track 100 hours total
.TP
.B Week Warrior
Track for 7 consecutive days
.TP
.B Month Master
Track for 30 consecutive days
.PP
And many more! Run \fBmateriatrack achievements\fR to see all.
